snippet: In an announcement Friday, a federal jury said it was unable to reach a consensus on whether a former soldier should be executed for killing his young daughter in Hawaii, which doesn't have the death penalty....

headline.print_headline: A Look at What's Next in Hawaii Death Penalty Case
headline.main: A Look at What's Next in Hawaii Death Penalty Case

lead_paragraph: In an announcement Friday, a federal jury said it was unable to reach a consensus on whether a former soldier should be executed for killing his young daughter in Hawaii, which doesn't have the death penalty.
